()LN
EL
SL
(NAME)LN
EL
SL
(     AddDrawobj - add line, rectangle or circle)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SYNOPSIS)LN
EL
SL
(     AddDrawobj \( line | rect | circle \) \( 2D | 3D \))LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DESCRIPTION)LN
EL
SL
(     Add a line, rectangle or circle for annotation.)LN
EL
SL
(     The first argument selects the type of drawing object.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     If the second argument is 2D, the object is placed)LN
EL
SL
(     at a default location and can be moved to the desired)LN
EL
SL
(     place. It will always keep its screen position and is)LN
EL
SL
(     not related to any atoms.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     If the second argument is 3D, a label is added for)LN
EL
SL
(     each molecule that has selected atoms. The initial)LN
EL
SL
(     position in space is calculated as the average of the)LN
EL
SL
(     coordinates of all selected atoms of the molecule. The)LN
EL
SL
(     positon relative to these atoms can be changed with)LN
EL
SL
(     the mouse or with the MoveDrawobj command.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The created primitives have the property "drawobj".)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(EXAMPLES)LN
EL
SL
(     AddDrawobj line 3D)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SEE ALSO)LN
EL
SL
(     SelectAtom, ColorPrim, LinePrim, StyleDrawobj,)LN
EL
SL
(     MoveDrawobj, RemovePrim, AddTitle, AddText)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DATE)LN
EL
SL
(     970930)LN
EL

