EL
SL
(NAME)LN
EL
SL
(     AddRes - add residue to molecule)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SYNOPSIS)LN
EL
SL
(     AddRes \( first | last \) name)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DESCRIPTION)LN
EL
SL
(     Add a residue as first or last residue of all selected)LN
EL
SL
(     molecules.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The new residue can only be docked properly if the)LN
EL
SL
(     coordinates of the 3 atoms that overlap for subsequent)LN
EL
SL
(     residues are known for the last residue. If this is)LN
EL
SL
(     not the case, which happens frequently if a coordinate)LN
EL
SL
(     file was read, the missing atom coordinates \(mostly)LN
EL
SL
(     the 'N' for proteints\) should be calculated with the)LN
EL
SL
(     CalcAtom command first.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(EXAMPLE)LN
EL
SL
(     AddRes last "ALA")LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SEE ALSO)LN
EL
SL
(     NewMol, SelectMol, CalcAtom, ChangeRes, RemoveRes)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
