()LN
EL
SL
(NAME)LN
EL
SL
(     AddSheet - add sheet for schematic drawing)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SYNOPSIS)LN
EL
SL
(     AddSheet)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DESCRIPTION)LN
EL
SL
(     Create a surface that serves as schematic drawing of)LN
EL
SL
(     a beta sheet. The surface will approximate all)LN
EL
SL
(     selected atoms that belong to the same sheet. An atom)LN
EL
SL
(     is considered belonging to a sheet if the residue it)LN
EL
SL
(     belongs to has the 'sheet' property set. Even if)LN
EL
SL
(     multiple atoms of one residue are selected, only one)LN
EL
SL
(     of them is taken for determining the surface, it is)LN
EL
SL
(     recommended to select just the CA atoms.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The surface will not exactly pass through the atoms,)LN
EL
SL
(     but a smoothing algorithm is applied. To get nice)LN
EL
SL
(     smoothing at the borders, it is good to select not)LN
EL
SL
(     just the sheet atoms, but also atoms that are adjacent)LN
EL
SL
(     to the sheet.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The command is very easy to use for structures that)LN
EL
SL
(     have just one beta sheet. Then the user can just)LN
EL
SL
(     select all CA atoms and execute the command, provided)LN
EL
SL
(     that the secondary structure is known from the PDB)LN
EL
SL
(     file or calculated using the CalcSecondary command.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     If a structure has multiple beta sheets, they have to)LN
EL
SL
(     be created one after the other. It is best to start)LN
EL
SL
(     with all CA selected, create one sheet, deselect the)LN
EL
SL
(     atoms belonging to that sheet, creating the second)LN
EL
SL
(     sheet, etc.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The created primitives have the property "sheet".)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(EXAMPLE)LN
EL
SL
(     AddSheet)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SEE ALSO)LN
EL
SL
(     ReadPdb, CalcSecondary, SelectAtom, DefPropRes,)LN
EL
SL
(     AddRibbon, ColorPrim, TintPrim, ShadePrim,)LN
EL
SL
(     RemovePrim)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DATE)LN
EL
SL
(     970723)LN
EL

grestore

