SL
(     Generate a report with angles between helix axes.)LN
EL
SL
(     Cylinders have to be added for all helices to be)LN
EL
SL
(     considered by this command, and at least two such)LN
EL
SL
(     cylinders have to be selected. The command will)LN
EL
SL
(     create a two-dimensional table with angles for all)LN
EL
SL
(     pairs, indexed with the primitive numbers of the)LN
EL
SL
(     cylinders.)LN
