SL
(     given as third argument, and calculating the RMSD)LN
EL
SL
(     of all 3 residue.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The ninth argument is a space separated list of)LN
EL
SL
(     property names. The local displacements will be)LN
EL
SL
