SL
()LN
EL
SL
(NAME)LN
EL
SL
(     FigRamach - Ramachandran plot)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SYNOPSIS)LN
EL
SL
(     FigRamach name name nameList)LN
EL
SL
(         \( none | normal | VAL-ILE-THR | GLY \))LN
EL
SL
(         \( dot | plus | cross | res | res_box |)LN
EL
SL
(         mol | mol_box \))LN
EL
SL
(         \( dot | plus | cross | res | res_box |)LN
EL
SL
(         mol | mol_box \))LN
EL
SL
(         \( 0 | 1\) \( 0 | 1 \))LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DESCRIPTION)LN
EL
SL
(     Create a Ramachandran plot with the first angle name)LN
EL
SL
(     on the x-axis and the second angle name on the y-axis.)LN
EL
SL
(     Only residues where both angles are selected are)LN
EL
SL
(     shown.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The third argument is a space separated list of)LN
EL
SL
(     alternative residues \(typically GLY\).)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The fourth argument selects the background \(allowed)LN
EL
SL
(     regions\). The allowed regions were determined from)LN
EL
SL
(     378 different crystal structures with a resolution)LN
EL
SL
(     of 2.5 A or better. The regions where the density)LN
EL
SL
(     of points \(PHI/PSI\) from this statistic is highest)LN
EL
SL
(     are marked with color. The green regions contain 80%)LN
EL
SL
(     of all points, the green and yellow regions together)LN
EL
SL
(     95%, all colored regions together 98%. There is a)LN
EL
SL
(     background for all non-GLY/PRO residues, one for)LN
EL
SL
(     VAL/ILE/THR and one for GLY.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The fifth argument selects the display style of)LN
EL
SL
(     residues not listed as alternative, the sixth)LN
EL
SL
(     argument the one for alternative residues.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     If the color option is selected, he colors of the)LN
EL
SL
(     markers is taken from the bond corresponding to the)LN
EL
SL
(     angle, otherwise they are all black.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     If the last option is selected and all angles shown)LN
EL
SL
(     in the plot have the same angle constraints, the)LN
EL
SL
(     allowed region is indicated in light grey.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The user can select residues by clicking on symbols)LN
EL
SL
(     in the plot.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(EXAMPLE)LN
EL
SL
(     FigRamach 'PHI' 'PSI' 'GLY' normal dot plus 1 0)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SEE ALSO)LN
EL
SL
(     ReadAco, SelectAngle, FigOff)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DATE)LN
EL
SL
(     960519)LN
EL

