EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SYNOPSIS)LN
EL
SL
(     MoveZ expr)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DESCRIPTION)LN
EL
SL
(     Move all movable \(set with DialMol\) molecules by the)LN
EL
SL
(     given amount in Z direction. Moving in Z direction is)LN
EL
SL
(     very similar to zooming, which is normally done)LN
EL
SL
(     interactively by pressing the left and the middle mouse)LN
EL
SL
(     buttons simultanously. The effect is somewhat different)LN
EL
SL
(     if a perspective projection is chosen, and also the)LN
EL
SL
(     clipping planes work differently.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(EXAMPLE)LN
EL
SL
(     MoveZ 10)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
