()LN
EL
SL
(     This command is not supported on all machines and)LN
EL
SL
(     with all graphics systems. It will give an appropriate)LN
EL
SL
(     error message if it is not supported.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The freely available PNG library written by)LN
EL
SL
(     Guy Eric Schalnat, Group 42, Inc., is used for writing)LN
EL
SL
(     the PNG file.)LN
