()LN
EL
SL
(NAME)LN
EL
SL
(     StyleRibbon - set display style of ribbons)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SYNOPSIS)LN
EL
SL
(     StyleRibbon \( invisible | rect | round |)LN
EL
SL
(         rounded | ellip | lense | as_is \))LN
EL
SL
(         [ \( open | sharp | soft | as_is \))LN
EL
SL
(         [ \( open | sharp | soft | arrow | as_is \))LN
EL
SL
(         [ \( const | atom | as_is \) ] ] ])LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DESCRIPTION)LN
EL
SL
(     Set the display style of all selected ribbons. The)LN
EL
SL
(     first argument gives the profile of the middle part,)LN
EL
SL
(     the optional second and third argument determine the)LN
EL
SL
(     style of the start and the end.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     The fourth argument only has an effect when the)LN
EL
SL
(     profile is 'round'. With the value 'atom', the radius)LN
EL
SL
(     is interpolated between the radii of the atoms used to)LN
EL
SL
(     define the spline, normally the CA atom for proteins.)LN
EL
SL
(     This can e. g. be used to show mobility by varying)LN
EL
SL
(     radius of the spline if the radius of the atoms is set)LN
EL
SL
(     to \(a function of\) the B-factor. For bundles of NMR)LN
EL
SL
(     structures, the B-factors can be calculated by)LN
EL
SL
(     MeanMol.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(     For all arguments, the value 'as_is' will leave the)LN
EL
SL
(     style unchanged, this is useful when one wants to)LN
EL
SL
(     change part of the values for multiple ribbons at)LN
EL
SL
(     once.)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(EXAMPLES)LN
EL
SL
(     StyleRibbon rect)LN
EL
SL
(     StyleRibbon rounded sharp arrow)LN
EL
SL
(     StyleRibbon round open open atom)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(SEE ALSO)LN
EL
SL
(     AddRibbon, SelectPrim, LengthPrim,)LN
EL
SL
(     TypeRibbon, SizeRibbon, PaintRibbon,)LN
EL
SL
(     MeanMol, RadiusAtom)LN
EL
SL
()LN
EL
SL
(DATE)LN
EL
SL
(     950509)LN
EL

